		    comment = c(ORCID="0000-0001-9499-8382")))
Maintainer: Adrian Baddeley <Adrian.Baddeley@curtin.edu.au>
Description: Extension to the 'spatstat' package, for analysing large datasets
	     of spatial points on a network. Provides a
	     memory-efficient algorithm for computing the
	     geometrically-corrected K function, described in
	     S. Rakshit, A. Baddeley and G. Nair (2019).
